title: Bunny meet Bunny Could Katie Price’s Instagram get any cuter
text:
Bunny meet Bunny: Could Katie Price’s Instagram get any cuter? 
Evoke.ie Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Katie Price is clearly a fan of all things fluffy and small, judging by her Instagram activity. 
The majority of her posts comprise of a) her pouting, b) babies or c) animals. 
And on Wednesday, Katie, 37, took to social media once again to upload a picture of one-year-old Bunny with – wait for it – an actual bunny!
